spring day 5
--------------------
                                                          Java-Based Configuration using AppConfig

🎯 Objective
Task 1 — School with Principal and Address Injection
🎯 Objective

Demonstrate multiple object injection using AppConfig in Spring 5 where a School depends on both Principal and Address objects.

🧱 Class-wise Design
1️.Principal Class

Attributes:

String name

int experience

Methods:

Setter methods and a display method to show principal details.

2️.Address Class

Attributes:

String city

String state

Methods:

Setter methods and a method to display address info.

3️.School Class

Attributes:

String schoolName

Principal principal

Address address

Methods:

Setter methods for all fields.

showDetails() method to display complete school information.

4️.AppConfig Class

Responsibilities:

Annotated with @Configuration.

Define beans for Principal, Address, and School.

Inject both Principal and Address beans into the School bean.

5️.MainApp Class

Responsibilities:

Load Spring context using AnnotationConfigApplicationContext.

Retrieve the School bean and call showDetails().

📘 Expected Output
========================
School: Sunshine High School
Principal: Dr. Anil Kumar (20 years experience)
Location: Hyderabad, Telangana